CISOutboundIntegrationContextForm is a Form
    Layout
        valid when (not YellowAlert)
            four column distributed
                column1 of 30%
                    IntegrationName
                    Description
                        use text area of 2 lines
                column2 of 20%
                    UseDefaultProcess
                        display as switch
                        initial value is true
                    visible when (not UseDefaultProcess)
                        Process
                            display as required
                column3 of 30%
                    paragraph
                        Status
                            display as text
                            raise red alert when (RedAlert)
                            raise yellow alert when (YellowAlert)
                            raise green alert when (GreenAlert)
                        button of "<PfiWorkunit>"
                            link is PfiWorkunit
                            display as link
                column4 of 20%
                    paragraph
                        Active
                            display only
